ining</span></h2><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-252_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-254_">Here at The Mandatory Training Group, we receive many questions about the CSTF aligned statutory and mandatory training courses. We have selected a few of these questions and answered them below.</span></p><div data-scrolling="false" data-multiple="false" data-pf-type="Accordion" class="sc-cNKqjZ diijrs pf-255_"><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-256_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-257_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="7d0dab91-ca2b-4f28-a451-e01be871300c" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>What is CSTF aligned statutory and mandatory training?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7d0dab91-ca2b-4f28-a451-e01be871300c" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-259_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-260_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-262_">CSTF aligned statutory and mandatory training is compulsory training determined under the UK Core Skills Training Framework ( UK CSTF) as essential for the safe and efficient delivery of healthcare services. Healthcare statutory and mandatory training is designed to reduce organisational risks and comply with current UK legislation, national guidance and local policies.
<br><br>The UK Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF) sets out 11 statutory and mandatory training topics for all staff working in health and social care settings. The CSTF includes nationally agreed learning outcomes and training delivery standards.
<br><br><span style="font-style: italic; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 102, 204);"><a href="/collections/online-mandatory-training-courses-cstf-mandatory-elearning-courses" target="_blank" style="">Click here to learn more about the statutory and mandatory training courses aligned to the UK Core Skills Training Framework (CSTF).</a></span></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-263_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-264_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="3d8da4ee-eba8-4c3b-b7d0-e18d4989fc38" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Did Skills for Health verify this CSTF statutory/mandatory training package?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="3d8da4ee-eba8-4c3b-b7d0-e18d4989fc38" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-266_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-267_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-269_">Yes. Skills for Health has verified this 'CSTF Mandatory + Statutory Training​​ Annual Refresher' training package to align with the UK Core Skills Training Framework (UKCSTF).</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-270_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-271_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="6afeed58-1d2f-493d-8da4-eeeba88c3b37" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the CSTF statutory/mandatory training package accredited?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="6afeed58-1d2f-493d-8da4-eeeba88c3b37" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-273_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-274_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-276_">Yes. The ‘CSTF Mandatory + Statutory Training​​ Annual Refresher’ was externally reviewed and accredited by the CPD Certification Service (CPDUK).</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-277_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-278_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="e87e2d36-a624-446a-beed-581d2f093d8d" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I still do the ‘All in One Day Mandatory Training’ package?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="e87e2d36-a624-446a-beed-581d2f093d8d" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-280_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-281_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-283_">Yes. You can still do the all in one day ‘Mandatory + Statutory’ training package. However, the one day statutory and mandatory bundle is not framework aligned.
<br><br>We recommend that you talk to your employer about which type of mandatory and statutory training you require.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-284_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-285_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="1b6ab273-2415-42e8-be2d-36a624846afe" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How do I book for the all in one day mandatory + statutory training?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="1b6ab273-2415-42e8-be2d-36a624846afe" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-287_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-288_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-290_">Book online to secure your place on the all in one day ‘Mandatory + Statutory Training’​​ annual refresher. Select the date a the top of this page and click the 'Book Now' button to be taken to the online booking form. <br><br>&nbsp;Please note that these courses fill up quickly!
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-291_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-292_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="06ef834c-024e-491b-aab2-73241562e87e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How often should I complete the one day mandatory + statutory training?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="06ef834c-024e-491b-aab2-73241562e87e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-294_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-295_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-297_">The all in one day ‘Mandatory + Statutory Training’ course must be completed annually.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-298_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-299_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="6c4a491e-18a8-4b06-af83-4c024e191b6a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Is the ‘Mandatory + Statutory Training’ course suitable for new care workers?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="6c4a491e-18a8-4b06-af83-4c024e191b6a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-301_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-302_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-304_">The all in one day ‘Mandatory + Statutory Training’ package is a yearly refresher course. It is not suitable for candidates who do not have prior experience.
<br><br>Health and care workers who are new to the sector must complete their initial statutory and mandatory training according to their organisation’s requirements.
<br><br>It is highly recommended that new health and social care support workers must complete the Care Certificate training programme within the first 12 weeks of their employment (as part of their induction and onboarding training). <br><br><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/products/care-certificate-15-online-training-courses-cpduk-accredited?variant=3953078725" target="_blank" style="font-style: italic;">Click on the link below to register for the online Care Certificate course:
The 'Care Certificate' Training Course - Skills for Care Aligned.
</a></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-AjmGg eCTxfx pf-305_"><button type="button" class="sc-dPiLbb jUujTN pf-306_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="d3ef0493-3ba3-446c-8a49-1e18a82b06ef" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Does the CSTF annual training day include practical demonstrations?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="d3ef0493-3ba3-446c-8a49-1e18a82b06ef" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-bBHHxi ezvCRe pf-308_"><p class="sc-iukxot iZqxsD pf-309_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hgKiOD hnskCB pf-311_">Yes. Our live virtual webinar-based annual mandatory + statutory training day includes the essential practical elements of manual handling objects, people moving and handling and cardiopulmonary resuscitation.
<br><br>We also provide live online classroom video-link courses (one-to-one) for cardiopulmonary resuscitation.
